\subsection{Reported cases}

Use the \code{jurisdiction} entry type for citing cases.

\tip{Use the \code{keyword} field to specify the jurisdiction. The following are recognized:
  \begin{itemize}
  \item\val{gb}
    United Kingdom
  \item\val{en}:
    England (default)
  \item\val{cy}:
    Wales
  \item\val{sc}:
    Scotland
  \item\val{ni}:
    Northern Ireland
  \item\val{eu}:
